<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-2716] Make Kafka core not depend on log4j-appender</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-2716</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Investigate why core needs to depend on log4j-appender. AFAIK, there is no real dependency, however it the dependency is removed, tests won&apos;t build it. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
